00:20:27.640 --> 00:20:31.930
for immigrants, especially when
you have a large hotel company

00:20:31.930 --> 00:20:34.930
that you need to
staff seasonally.

00:20:34.930 --> 00:20:37.540
And it's become
something that's been

00:20:37.540 --> 00:20:40.510
very troublesome, especially
for the travel and tourism

00:20:40.510 --> 00:20:41.309
industry.

00:20:41.309 --> 00:20:42.100
JESSE HAINES: Yeah.

00:20:42.100 --> 00:20:46.330
Have you seen other corporations
or business leaders sort

00:20:46.330 --> 00:20:51.580
of really stepping out on
this topic in ways that have

00:20:51.580 --> 00:20:54.587
been meaningful and impactful?

00:20:54.587 --> 00:20:56.670
ANDREW TISCH: We're starting
to see more and more.

00:20:56.670 --> 00:20:58.300
The Chamber of
