00:20:58.300 --> 00:20:59.990
to get more vocal about it.

00:20:59.990 --> 00:21:05.690
And you're starting
to hear more people.

00:21:05.690 --> 00:21:10.540
And I think as the
labor pool tightens up,

00:21:10.540 --> 00:21:15.220
you'll hear more and more
senior executives, who

00:21:15.220 --> 00:21:17.565
can't get the right
people, comment about it.

00:21:17.565 --> 00:21:19.990
JESSE HAINES: Right.

