00:28:37.636 --> 00:28:39.160
They were born here.

00:28:39.160 --> 00:28:41.910
And so to someone
like them, especially

00:28:41.910 --> 00:28:45.510
a lot of Trump voters, we
know, it is not the same

00:28:45.510 --> 00:28:47.580
as saying, here's a Danish guy.

00:28:47.580 --> 00:28:50.920
